t the Mediterranean littoral, this volume contains something of interest for numerous areas of investigation, including comparative Semitics, Anatolian, early Mediterranean, and even Hebrew and biblical studies.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 7aHISTORY / Ancient / General.2bisacsh1 aGzella, Holger, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHasselbach, Rebecca, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHolmstedt, Robert D., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHolmstedt, Robert D., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKerr, Robert M., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMosca, Paul G., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOtero, Andrés Piquer, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPardee, Dennis, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPat-El, Naʾama, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchade, Aaron, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchade, Aaron, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSchmitz, Philip C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPenn State University Press Complete eBook-Package Pre-2014z978311074526940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781575068558?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781575068558423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781575068558/original  a978-3-11-074526-9  Penn State University Press Complete eBook-Package Pre-2014b2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_CL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGB